responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "670F3B5840A67ADA9A2538B0CB6030CB", "Take the elixir and the words, for they are your guide. To the Ancestral Hollow you must go, where the earth and sky meet. There, the Horn's curse will be undone. When the time is right, speak the words and let the elixir's glow lead the way. The spirits will listen, but only if your purpose is true.")
